Mortal Kombat;;57;;45;;PG-13;;Lord Rayden (Christopher Lambert) handpicks three martial artists -- federal agent Sonya Blade (Bridgette Wilson), Shaolin monk Lui Kang (Robin Shou) and action movie sensation Johnny Cage (Linden Ashby) -- and mentors them. After intense training, Rayden transports the trio to Outworld, the site of an inter-dimensional fighting tournament. There, the three humans must defeat the demonic warriors of the evil Shang Sung (Cary-Hiroyuki Tagawa) -- or allow Sung to take over the Earth.;;Action;;Paul W.S. Anderson;;1995;;Robin Shou,Linden Ashby,Bridgette Wilson-Sampras,Cary-Hiroyuki Tagawa,Talisa Soto,Christopher Lambert,Trevor Goddard,Chris Casamassa;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mortal_kombat